TY 鍵盤，而防破裂玻璃錶面比上代強化，是歷來最堅固耐用，除了繼續支持 50m 防水，更加是首款獲得 IP6X 防塵認證的 Apple Watch。Apple Watch Series 7 充電後可以使用 18 小時，以充電速度亦快了 33%。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/10/05/facebook-outage-instagram-whatsapp-messenger/life-tech/social-network/attachment/1005-3b-4/" rel="attachment wp-att-1063857"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1063857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b-1280x640.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b-768x384.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1005-3b.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>Apple Watch Series 7 系列會提供午夜暗色、星光色、綠色、藍色和 (PRODUCT)RED 紅色 5 種鋁金屬錶殼、銀色、石墨色和金色 3 款不鏽鋼錶殼，至於 Apple Watch Edition 則有鈦金屬及太空黑鈦金屬錶殼可供選擇。Apple 同時宣佈 Apple Watch Nike 和 Apple Watch Hermès 亦推出了全新獨家錶帶及錶面，Apple Watch Series 7 售價由 HK$3,199 起。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2021/10/apple-watch-series-7-orders-start-friday-october-8/">Apple</a></p>
